{"id":"api/core/HostBinding","title":"HostBinding","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/HostBinding\", \"name\": \"HostBinding\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1289-L1289\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1289-L1289\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"hostbinding\">HostBinding<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#hostbinding\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一個裝飾器，用於把一個 DOM 屬性標記為繫結到宿主的屬性，並提供配置元資料。Angular 在變更檢測期間會自動檢查宿主屬性繫結，如果這個繫結變化了，它就會更新該指令所在的宿主元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Decorator that marks a DOM property as a host-binding property and supplies configuration\nmetadata.\nAngular automatically checks host property bindings during change detection, and\nif a binding changes it updates the host element of the directive.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>選項</th><th>說明</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#hostPropertyName\">\n          <code>hostPropertyName?</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">要繫結到資料屬性的 DOM 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The DOM property that is bound to a data property.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"hostPropertyName\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"hostpropertyname\">hostPropertyName<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#hostpropertyname\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1275-L1281\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1275-L1281\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">要繫結到資料屬性的 DOM 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The DOM property that is bound to a data property.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            hostPropertyName?: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">下面的例子建立了一個指令，它會對具有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a></code> 指令的 DOM 元素設定 <code>valid</code> 和 <code>invalid</code> 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example creates a directive that sets the <code>valid</code> and <code>invalid</code>\nproperties on the DOM element that has an <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a></code> directive on it.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: '[<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]'})\nclass NgModelStatus {\n  constructor(public control: <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModel</a>) {}\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('class.valid') get valid() { return this.control.valid; }\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('class.invalid') get invalid() { return this.control.invalid; }\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: `&lt;input [(<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>)]=\"prop\"&gt;`,\n})\nclass App {\n  prop;\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations/trigger\n - api/core\n - guide/add-an-animation\n - guide/animations\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/elements\n - guide/migration-undecorated-classes\n - guide/style-precedence\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/transition-and-triggers\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/HostBinding#hostPropertyName\n - api/core/HostBinding#hostbinding\n - api/core/HostBinding#hostpropertyname\n - api/core/HostBinding#options\n - api/core/HostBinding#usage-notes\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1275-L1281\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1289-L1289\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1275-L1281\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1289-L1289\n-->"}